'''拳头游戏'''（{{lang-en|Riot Games}}），又称'''拳头公司'''或'''拳頭社'''或'''R社'''，台灣註冊商號名為「'''銳玩遊戲'''」<ref>{{cite web|url=https://yellowpage.fixy.com.tw/company/information/%E9%8A%B3%E7%8E%A9%E9%81%8A%E6%88%B2%E6%9C%89%E9%99%90%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8-24558619/1895224|2=|title=銳玩遊戲有限公司|accessdate=2018-01-16|archive-date=2018-01-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180116193452/https://yellowpage.fixy.com.tw/company/information/%E9%8A%B3%E7%8E%A9%E9%81%8A%E6%88%B2%E6%9C%89%E9%99%90%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8-24558619/1895224|dead-url=no}}</ref>，是一間[[美国|美国]][[电子游戏|电子游戏]][[電子遊戲開發商|开发商]]和[[電子遊戲發行商|发行商]]。公司成立于2006年，其总部位于美国[[加利福尼亚州|加利福尼亚州]][[圣莫尼卡|圣莫尼卡]]。另外並有辦公室分佈在[[柏林|柏林]]、[[都柏林|都柏林]]、[[香港|香港]]、[[伊斯坦堡|伊斯坦布尔]]、[[墨西哥市|墨西哥城]]、[[莫斯科|莫斯科]]、[[紐約市|纽约市]]、[[圣路易斯_(密苏里州)|聖路易斯]]、[[首爾|首尔]]、[[上海|上海]]、[[新加坡|新加坡]]、[[悉尼|悉尼]]、[[台北|台北]]和[[東京|东京]]。

拳头游戏的著名作品《[[英雄联盟|英雄联盟]]》发行于2009年10月<ref>{{cite web|author=Riot Games|title=LEAGUE OF LEGENDS LAUNCHES!|url=http://www.riotgames.com/articles/20091007/260/league-legends-here|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140222133616/http://www.riotgames.com/articles/20091007/260/league-legends-here|archivedate=2014年2月22日}}</ref>，在2013年有近3千万的日活跃玩家<ref>{{cite web|author=Eddie Makuch|title=League of Legends now boasts 27 million daily players|url=http://www.gamespot.com/articles/league-of-legends-now-boasts-27-million-daily-players/1100-6417374/|publisher=GameSpot|accessdate=2014-02-16|archive-date=2014-02-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140202110609/http://www.gamespot.com/articles/league-of-legends-now-boasts-27-million-daily-players/1100-6417374/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2015年12月17日，[[腾讯公司|腾讯公司]]收购 Riot Games 全數股權，Riot Games 繼而成为了腾讯旗下的子公司。Riot games其他的作品包含手機遊戲《[[英雄聯盟普羅快跑|英雄聯盟普羅快跑]]》、《[[英雄聯盟：激鬥峽谷|英雄聯盟：激鬥峽谷]]》（即《英雄联盟手游》）、《[[聯盟戰棋|聯盟戰棋]]》<ref>{{cite web |author1=拳头公司 |title=云顶之弈 |url=http://lol.qq.com/act/a20191029tftset2/index.html?e_code=494836&idataid=282138 |website=云顶之弈 |publisher=腾讯 |accessdate=2020-01-17 |archive-date=2021-04-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210411034500/http://lol.qq.com/act/a20191029tftset2/index.html?e_code=494836&idataid=282138 |dead-url=no }}</ref>、網頁遊戲《[[科加斯吃了全世界|科加斯吃了全世界]]》等。

==概述==
拳头游戏作为一个独立的游戏工作室于2006年由布兰登·雷兹·贝克（Brandon "Ryze" Beck）和马克·泰达米尔·美林（Marc "Tryndamere" Merrill）创立<ref>{{cite web|author=Kath Brice|title=Blizzard developers join Riot Games' online title|url=http://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/blizzard-developers-join-riot-games-online-title|publisher=GamesIndustry|accessdate=2014-02-16|archive-date=2013-10-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131016061923/http://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/blizzard-developers-join-riot-games-online-title|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2008年10月该公司宣布了其第一款游戏——《英雄联盟：命运冲突》（''League of Legends: Clash of Fates''）<ref>{{cite web|author=Anthony Gallegos|title=Riot Games' League of Legends Announced|url=http://www.1up.com/news/riot-games-league-legends-announced|publisher=1up|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131017013542/http://www.1up.com/news/riot-games-league-legends-announced|archivedate=2013-10-17}}</ref>，并在一年后以《英雄联盟》为名发布。游戏采用[[网络游戏免费模式|免费游戏]]、[[微收费|道具收費]]的模式盈利。

2008年，拳头游戏从[[风险投资|风险投资]]公司{{link-en|Benchmark Capital|Benchmark Capital}}和{{link-en|FirstMark Capital|FirstMark Capital}}处获得了7百万美元的启动资金<ref>{{cite web|url=http://kotaku.com/5023761/riot-games-get-a-7m-launch|title=Riot Games Get a $7M Launch|publisher=Kotaku|author=Leigh Alexander|date=2008-07-10|accessdate=2013-10-16|archive-date=2013-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131108153943/http://kotaku.com/5023761/riot-games-get-a-7m-launch|dead-url=no}}</ref>；2009年第二轮融资中，再次融得Benchmark、FirstMark以及[[腾讯控股|腾讯控股]]8百万美元投资<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.pehub.com/2009/09/09/riot-games-raises-8-million/|title=Riot Games Raises $8 Million|publisher=PE Hub|author=admin|date=2009-09-09|accessdate=2013-10-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131016104103/http://www.pehub.com/2009/09/09/riot-games-raises-8-million/|archive-date=2013-10-16|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://connection.ebscohost.com/c/articles/44167965/riot-games-8-million-play|title=Riot Games: $8 Million to Play With|publisher=Red Herring|author=Lalee Sadighi|date=Sep 2009|accessdate=2013-10-16|archive-date=2014-10-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141027032112/http://connection.ebscohost.com/c/articles/44167965/riot-games-8-million-play|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|author=宋鹏展|title=腾讯等800万美元注资网游出版商Riot Games|url=http://www.wabei.cn/news/200909/273903.html|accessdate=2014-02-16|newspaper=挖贝网|date=2009-09-16|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20140216231148/http://www.wabei.cn/news/200909/273903.html|archivedate=2014-02-16}}</ref>。2011年2月，腾讯以总交易金额16.79亿元人民币（其中包含现金15.25亿元和1.55亿元股权）增持Riot Games，持股比例由交易前的22.34%增至92.78%<ref name=netease>{{cite news|author=李好宇|title=腾讯投资Riot Games一年亏损8.2亿元|url=http://tech.163.com/12/0314/22/7SJD53NT000915BF.html|accessdate=2014-02-16|newspaper=网易|date=2012-03-14|archive-date=2014-02-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140222044031/http://tech.163.com/12/0314/22/7SJD53NT000915BF.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。本次交易对RiotGames估值约21.68亿元人民币<ref name=netease/>。[[彭博商业周刊|彭博商业周刊]]和[[VentureBeat|VentureBeat]]估计交易额大约为3.5至4亿美元<ref>{{cite web|url=http://allthingsd.com/20110204/chinas-tencent-buys-riot-games-for-400-million/|title=China's Tencent Buys Riot Games|author=Peter Kafka|publisher=All Things Digital|date=2011-02-04|accessdate=2013-10-16|archive-date=2013-10-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131016213515/http://allthingsd.com/20110204/chinas-tencent-buys-riot-games-for-400-million/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/02/05/riotgames-tencent-idUSN044616620110205 | work=Reuters | first=Clare | last=Baldwin | title=UPDATE 1-Tencent acquires majority stake in Riot Games | date=2011-02-05 | accessdate=2013-10-16 | archive-date=2014-02-14 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140214052727/http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/02/05/riotgames-tencent-idUSN044616620110205 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。腾讯随后公布此次交易金额为$231,465,000<ref>{{cite web|url=http://tencent.com/en-us/content/ir/rp/2011/attachments/201101.pdf |title=Tencent 2011 Interim Report |page=44 |publisher=Tencent |accessdate=2014-01-29 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140308024641/http://tencent.com/en-us/content/ir/rp/2011/attachments/201101.pdf |archivedate=2014-03-08 }}</ref>。完成此次交易后，Riot Games成为腾讯旗下[[子公司|子公司]]，仍由原创始人及管理团队全权负责，独立运作<ref>{{cite news|author=李好宇|title=腾讯收购Riot Games细节：现金支出2.31亿美元|url=http://tech.163.com/11/1109/21/7IEU6NL3000915BF.html|accessdate=2014-02-16|newspaper=网易|archive-date=2014-02-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140222043924/http://tech.163.com/11/1109/21/7IEU6NL3000915BF.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2015年12月16日，Riot Games透過部落格提到中國騰訊買下其全部股份，使Riot Games將成為騰訊的全資子公司<ref>{{cite news|author=Juro Osawa|title=騰訊收購其尚未持有的網遊公司Riot Games全部股份|url=http://cn.wsj.com/big5/20151217/tec165728.asp|accessdate=2015-12-17|newspaper=華爾街日報|archive-date=2015-12-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151222094649/http://cn.wsj.com/big5/20151217/tec165728.asp|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thescoreesports.com/lol/news/5378|title=Tencent purchases remaining shares in Riot Games to hold 100% of equity|first=Kelsey|last=Moser|website=TheScore eSports|publisher=TheScore Inc.|date=2015-12-16|accessdate=2015-12-18|archive-date=2015-12-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151218044128/http://www.thescoreesports.com/lol/news/5378|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.polygon.com/2015/12/16/10326320/riot-games-now-owned-entirely-by-tencent|title=Riot Games now owned entirely by Tencent|first=Allegra|last=Frank|website=[[Polygon_(website)|Polygon]]|date=2015-12-16|accessdate=2015-12-16|archive-date=2015-12-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151218235713/http://www.polygon.com/2015/12/16/10326320/riot-games-now-owned-entirely-by-tencent|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

拳头游戏的雇员中有来自原《[[DotA|DotA]]》的制作人员，比如前首席开发者[[史蒂夫·费克|史蒂夫·费克]]（Guinsoo）和前官方DotA-Allstars.com网站建立者Steve "Pendragon" Mescon<ref name=da>{{cite web|url=http://www.neutralcreeps.com/2011/07/steve-mescon-hints-bringing-dota.html|title=Steve Mescon hints bringing DotA-AllStars.com back online|publisher=Neutral Creeps|date=2011-07-05|accessdate=2013-10-16|archive-date=2013-10-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131016070540/http://www.neutralcreeps.com/2011/07/steve-mescon-hints-bringing-dota.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。Riot Games还雇用了一些前[[暴雪娱乐|暴雪娱乐]]的员工<ref name=blizzardEmployees>{{cite web|url=http://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/blizzard-developers-join-riot-games-online-title|title=Blizzard developers join Riot Games' online title|publisher=GamesIndustryInternational|author=Kath Brice|date=2009-06-25|accessdate=2013-10-16|archive-date=2013-10-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131016061923/http://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/blizzard-developers-join-riot-games-online-title|dead-url=no}}</ref>，包括《[[魔兽世界|魔兽世界]]》前首席系统设计师[[格雷格·斯特里特|格雷格·斯特里特]]<ref>{{cite news|author=Paul Tassi|title=Greg 'Ghostcrawler' Street Jumps From Blizzard To Riot Games|url=http://www.forbes.com/sites/insertcoin/2014/01/14/greg-ghostcrawler-street-jumps-from-blizzard-to-riot-games/|accessdate=2014-02-16|newspaper=Forbes|archive-date=2014-02-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140219072503/http://www.forbes.com/sites/insertcoin/2014/01/14/greg-ghostcrawler-street-jumps-from-blizzard-to-riot-games/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2013年11月8日，拳头游戏宣布將會移動其總部到西洛杉磯的一棟新大樓。

2015年12月16日，拳头游戏將其剩餘的資產賣給騰訊。

2016年3月8日，拳头游戏宣布收购[[Radiant_Entertainment|Radiant Entertainment]]。<ref name="polygon-radiantacquired">{{cite web|title=Riot Games acquires Rising Thunder and Stonehearth studio Radiant Entertainment|url=http://www.polygon.com/2016/3/8/11181204/riot-games-acquires-radiant-entertainment|website=Polygon|publisher=Vox Media|accessdate=2016-03-08|archive-date=2016-09-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160928030947/http://www.polygon.com/2016/3/8/11181204/riot-games-acquires-radiant-entertainment|dead-url=no}}</ref>
